334
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:58,370
Who are you?

335
00:20:58,370 --> 00:21:00,420
I’m known

336
00:21:00,420 --> 00:21:01,900
as Black Judge.

337
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:04,300
Why don’t you be White Reaper

338
00:21:04,300 --> 00:21:05,940
and my apprentice?

339
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:09,370
Say it again!

340
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:11,890
You have good martial arts.

341
00:21:13,330 --> 00:21:16,300
Why does Chongxiao always protect you?

342
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:18,580
What do you mean by protecting me?

343
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:20,460
I ran after him all the way here.

344
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:22,210
He took my whisk

345
00:21:22,210 --> 00:21:23,850
and hid in the mountains.

346
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:26,490
Finally, he went down the mountain

347
00:21:26,490 --> 00:21:28,090
and visited the blacksmith’s shop

348
00:21:28,090 --> 00:21:29,850
to forge scabbards.

349
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:31,780
He forged a dozen scabbards.

350
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:34,850
He’s the chief of Qi School.

351
00:21:34,850 --> 00:21:37,460
But he did such a stupid thing

352
00:21:37,460 --> 00:21:39,580
