353
00:21:39,580 --> 00:21:41,010
Isn’t it funny?

354
00:21:48,730 --> 00:21:49,900
Psychopath!

355
00:21:54,300 --> 00:21:56,700
You killed him?

356
00:22:04,090 --> 00:22:06,210
