358
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:21,900
<i>Lingling</i>

359
00:22:54,730 --> 00:22:56,130
Young Master.

360
00:22:56,130 --> 00:22:57,610
My Lady.

361
00:22:57,610 --> 00:22:58,940
When we’re in Lingling Town,

362
00:22:58,940 --> 00:23:00,490
we’re within the territory
of the Huo family.

363
00:23:00,490 --> 00:23:02,060
At the Demon-Extermination Assembly
in a few days,

364
00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:04,090
you must be very cautious
with your words and actions.

365
00:23:04,090 --> 00:23:06,300
Don’t offend Junior Master Huo.

366
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:07,700
Don’t worry, Mr. Lin.

367
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:09,420
I hear everybody else goes there,

368
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:11,660
for the ripple pattern.

369
00:23:11,660 --> 00:23:13,660
<i>Zhu Chen, Xingnan Sect</i>
We’re not interested in that.

370
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:15,420
We’ll be fine.

371
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,700
Brother.

372
00:23:16,700 --> 00:23:18,610
Then why did you leave
all business behind

373
00:23:18,610 --> 00:23:20,540
