after receiving the invitation?

374
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,210
<i>Zhu Ying, Xingnan Sect</i>
We don’t have great martial arts.

375
00:23:22,210 --> 00:23:24,610
<i>Zhu Ying, Xingnan Sect</i>
We can’t help much to fight the Demons.

376
00:23:24,610 --> 00:23:26,250
Why must we come?

377
00:23:26,250 --> 00:23:27,940
Ying, don’t talk nonsense.

378
00:23:28,210 --> 00:23:31,010
Old Master Huo’s been nice to us.

379
00:23:31,010 --> 00:23:32,180
Thanks to them,

380
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:34,580
we have no problem
doing business in the south.

381
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:36,180
We received the invitation.

382
00:23:36,180 --> 00:23:36,940
Anyway,

383
00:23:36,940 --> 00:23:39,090
we should come
and support Junior Master Huo.

384
00:23:49,300 --> 00:23:50,970
What are you looking at?

385
00:24:02,540 --> 00:24:03,900
It’s summer.

386
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:05,820
But that man is shivering with cold.

387
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:07,180
Is he sick?

388
00:24:07,180 --> 00:24:08,610
Ying, go.

389
00:24:08,610 --> 00:24:10,490
Take out a robe from our luggage

390
00:24:10,490 --> 00:24:12,130
and give it to that man.

391
00:24:12,300 --> 00:24:14,060
You’re trying to help people again.

392
00:24:25,700 --> 00:24:27,010
My brother asked me to give this to you.

393
00:24:33,610 --> 00:24:34,540
Thank you.

394
00:24:37,130 --> 00:24:37,850
Thank you.

395
00:24:37,850 --> 00:24:38,900
You’re welcome.

396
00:24:58,940 --> 00:25:04,660
<i>Lingling Inn</i>

397
00:25:17,660 --> 00:25:19,700
Why are the coins so cold?

398
00:25:20,210 --> 00:25:21,890
What are you doing? Robbing?

399
00:25:22,140 --> 00:25:24,420
<i>Animal characters made by CG</i>

400
00:25:26,250 --> 00:25:26,830
Go back.

401
00:25:26,840 --> 00:25:27,660
<i>Animal characters made by CG</i>

402
