<i>Poisoner Ying Hecong</i>

404
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:04,060
<i>Lingling Inn</i>

405
00:26:20,490 --> 00:26:22,060
Miss, how many of you are there?

406
00:26:22,060 --> 00:26:23,010
Just me.

407
00:26:23,010 --> 00:26:24,300
Come in, please.

408
00:26:24,300 --> 00:26:26,010
Come on. This way, please.

409
00:26:53,130 --> 00:26:54,180
Come in, please.

410
00:26:54,580 --> 00:26:55,300
Young Master.

411
00:26:55,300 --> 00:26:56,820
That girl killed people before.

412
00:26:56,820 --> 00:26:58,010
Don’t stare at her.

413
00:27:04,060 --> 00:27:06,460
Miss, are you with Cloud Ravine?

414
00:27:08,700 --> 00:27:10,090
I’m with Blue Bat.

415
00:27:10,090 --> 00:27:11,490
You’re just in time.

416
00:27:11,490 --> 00:27:12,820
There was a customer,

417
00:27:12,820 --> 00:27:15,330
looking like the man you’re after.

418
00:27:15,330 --> 00:27:17,180
He left the coins.

419
00:27:20,610 --> 00:27:22,610
They’re not special.

420
00:27:22,610 --> 00:27:24,300
But when he gave them to me,

421
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:25,700
they were cold as ice.

422
00:27:29,970 --> 00:27:31,370
Where has he gone?

423
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:32,580
I’m sorry,

424
00:27:32,580 --> 00:27:34,420
but I don’t know.

425
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:35,900
These days, people come and go

426
00:27:35,900 --> 00:27:38,330
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

427
00:27:38,330 --> 00:27:41,370
I’m afraid you can’t catch up with him.

428
00:27:41,370 --> 00:27:43,090
But since he’s in town,

429
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:45,540
he needs accommodation and traffic.

430
00:27:45,540 --> 00:27:48,660
Our business covers half of
the basic needs.

431
00:27:48,660 --> 00:27:50,090
The man you’re after...

432
00:27:50,090 --> 00:27:52,540
He could be negligent,
however careful he is.

433
00:27:52,540 --> 00:27:55,130
Why don’t you stay in our inn

434
00:27:55,130 --> 00:27:56,490
and wait for more news?

435
00:27:57,700 --> 00:27:58,850
Fine.

436
00:27:59,330 --> 00:28:00,370
Thanks, then.

437
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:06,820
Isn’t he supposed

438
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:09,460
to be in the south for sunlight?

439
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:13,210
Why did he come here?

440
00:28:23,180 --> 00:28:24,400
Let’s sit there.

441
00:28:25,060 --> 00:28:25,850
Waiter...

442
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:36,130
Get up. Get up.

443
00:28:36,130 --> 00:28:38,250
I don’t like the food in this inn.

444
00:28:38,250 --> 00:28:39,460
You tried any before?

445
00:28:39,460 --> 00:28:41,060
I don’t like it.
Let’s try another restaurant.

446
00:28:41,060 --> 00:28:43,300
Miss, our food tastes good.

447
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:44,460
Shut up!

448
00:28:46,370 --> 00:28:48,130
I... I mean...

449
00:28:48,130 --> 00:28:49,330
We’ll discuss about it

450
00:28:49,330 --> 00:28:51,090
and order the dishes later.

451
00:28:51,090 --> 00:28:52,210
Fine. Fine.

452
00:28:54,010 --> 00:28:55,010
Sit down.

453
00:29:01,300 --> 00:29:02,210
Who?

454
00:29:02,210 --> 00:29:03,060
No one.

455
00:29:08,610 --> 00:29:09,970
Zhou Fei!

456
00:29:11,090 --> 00:29:11,940
What are you doing?

457
00:29:11,940 --> 00:29:13,130
What are you doing?

458
00:29:13,130 --> 00:29:14,820
I want to challenge her.

459
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:16,130
We come for
the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

460
00:29:16,130 --> 00:29:17,130
If you challenge her,

461
00:29:17,130 --> 00:29:17,970
she’ll see us!

462
00:29:17,970 --> 00:29:19,130
Bonehead!

463
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:21,180
We?

464
00:29:21,460 --> 00:29:22,660
You come for it, right?

465
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:24,970
I only come to challenge Zhou Fei!

466
00:29:26,970 --> 00:29:28,300
Don’t go.

467
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:33,060
<i>Lingling Inn</i>

468
00:30:03,820 --> 00:30:05,900
Who are they?

469
00:30:05,900 --> 00:30:08,090
They’re with Four-guardian Mountain.

470
00:30:08,090 --> 00:30:10,420
I met them once.

471
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:12,940
They’re with Tortoise Master.

472
00:30:15,420 --> 00:30:17,940
They look strange.

473
00:30:17,940 --> 00:30:20,210
Why are they wearing the mourning?

474
00:30:21,610 --> 00:30:23,940
I hear Tortoise Master Ding Kui

475
00:30:23,940 --> 00:30:26,210
isn’t a good man.

476
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:46,610
Are you from Xingnan Sect?

477
00:30:46,610 --> 00:30:48,850
We have something important to tell you.

478
00:30:48,850 --> 00:30:51,130
Give us the invitation

479
00:30:51,130 --> 00:30:52,420
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

480
00:30:53,780 --> 00:30:56,700
Robbing in the inn in broad daylight?

481
00:30:56,700 --> 00:30:58,090
How lawless you are!

482
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:00,780
We want the invitation,

483
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:02,370
just because we don’t like it

484
00:31:02,370 --> 00:31:05,730
when you run errands
for Huo Liantao, the hypocrite.

485
00:31:06,730 --> 00:31:09,730
When he’s holding
the Demon-Extermination Assembly,

486
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:12,130
you even bring a cart of gifts to him.

487
00:31:13,850 --> 00:31:14,580
Will your cousin

488
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:16,970
help those people?

489
00:31:16,970 --> 00:31:19,940
She’s here looking for Xie Yun,
instead of fighting.

490
00:31:19,940 --> 00:31:21,660
They’re having a dog-fight.

491
00:31:21,660 --> 00:31:23,060
Why must she interfere?

492
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:26,210
You want to interfere?

493
00:31:26,210 --> 00:31:27,180
You...!

494
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:30,580
We’re just passing by

495
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:33,010
and teasing Huo Liantao’s dogs.

496
00:31:34,130 --> 00:31:35,570
What?

497
00:31:36,490 --> 00:31:38,370
Our sect is famous
for martial arts, too.

498
00:31:38,370 --> 00:31:39,940
Stop slandering us!

499
00:31:40,850 --> 00:31:42,420
Young girl.

500
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:44,180
Who are you?

501
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:46,210
When Old Master Zhu was in charge,

502
00:31:46,210 --> 00:31:49,460
your family could barely
be a famous sect.

503
00:31:49,460 --> 00:31:52,610
Since he was paralyzed in bed,

504
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:55,660
you’ve failed to do martial arts

505
00:31:55,660 --> 00:31:58,180
and have even done business for living.

506
00:31:58,180 --> 00:32:01,210
How can you still say
you’re martial artists?

507
00:32:01,210 --> 00:32:03,090
Oh, look at the invalid.

508
00:32:03,090 --> 00:32:04,820
He could never practice martial arts.

509
00:32:04,820 --> 00:32:06,900
He’s as weak as a girl.

510
00:32:07,180 --> 00:32:08,850
I mean, not even as weak as a girl.

511
00:32:08,850 --> 00:32:11,370
No wonder you must ingratiate yourselves
with Huo Liantao.

512
00:32:11,370 --> 00:32:13,540
Without his help,

513
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:16,820
your family would have disappeared.

514
00:32:17,730 --> 00:32:18,380
Ying.

515
00:32:22,250 --> 00:32:24,490
I don’t care when you slander me.

516
00:32:24,490 --> 00:32:26,420
But when you slander Junior Master Huo

517
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:28,850
in Lingling Town,

518
00:32:28,850 --> 00:32:30,490
don’t you fear you’ll cause problem?

519
00:32:30,490 --> 00:32:32,180
Problem?

520
00:32:32,180 --> 00:32:34,660
Don’t you know

521
00:32:34,660 --> 00:32:36,370
how he became the master of Huo’s Manor?

522
00:32:36,370 --> 00:32:38,060
Even before

523
00:32:38,060 --> 00:32:39,330
the Demons arrived,

524
00:32:39,330 --> 00:32:42,610
Huo Liantao ran away with fear,

525
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:45,090
leaving his huge properties behind.

526
00:32:45,090 --> 00:32:48,130
How shameless he is!

527
00:32:48,130 --> 00:32:49,900
And he dares

528
00:32:50,300 --> 00:32:53,300
to send out invitations?

529
00:32:53,300 --> 00:32:56,330
You’d better give us the invitation,

530
00:32:56,330 --> 00:32:57,300
so that we can challenge Huo Liantao

531
00:32:57,300 --> 00:33:01,540
on your behalf.

532
00:33:06,780 --> 00:33:09,420
Young man, don’t be nervous.

533
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:11,900
I won’t eat your young master.

534
00:33:15,490 --> 00:33:16,970
Since you’re Junior Master Huo’s enemy，

535
00:33:16,970 --> 00:33:18,460
you can fight with him.

536
00:33:18,460 --> 00:33:20,210
We are mere businessmen.

537
00:33:20,210 --> 00:33:21,900
And we haven’t offended you.

538
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:23,420
When you don’t dare
to fight him directly,

539
00:33:23,420 --> 00:33:24,460
you give vent on us.

540
00:33:24,460 --> 00:33:25,660
What do you think you’re doing?

541
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:27,900
Bullying the weak
and being scare of the strong?

542
00:33:28,610 --> 00:33:31,460
You think you can bully
whoever you want?

543
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:33,250
Let me say it again.

544
00:33:33,250 --> 00:33:35,250
Give me the invitation,

545
00:33:35,250 --> 00:33:38,250
and I’ll let you go.

546
00:33:38,250 --> 00:33:40,820
The invitation is for my family.

547
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:41,970
Even if you kill me,

548
00:33:41,970 --> 00:33:43,010
I won’t give it to you

549
00:33:43,010 --> 00:33:44,700
in case you deceive others!

550
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:45,730
Evil!

551
00:33:45,730 --> 00:33:46,940
You defamed my family

552
00:33:46,940 --> 00:33:48,610
and hurt our men so brutally!

553
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:55,940
Mr. Zhu.

554
00:33:55,940 --> 00:33:59,130
Which matters more,
your sister or the invitation?

555
00:33:59,130 --> 00:34:01,210
